    scheme and default values that SDL, SDL2 and X11 drivers use:
    [screen]
      screentype=5            ; 0=80x25, 1=80x30, 2=80x50, 3=80x60,
      4=132x25, 5=132x30, 6=132x50, 7=132x60, 8=custom
